phase2.explanation:
You created a button but never added it to the layout!

FIX: Add the button to the layout:
VBox root = new VBox();
root.getChildren().add(button);
Scene scene = new Scene(root, 300, 200);

Or add directly when creating scene:
Scene scene = new Scene(new VBox(button), 300, 200);

Always remember to add controls to the scene graph!

